Modifications made to the original code:

1. Framework Change
   - Replaced web-based interface (JavaScript/Python backend) with PyQt6 desktop application
   - Changed from online storage to local data storage

2. Data Source
   - Uses bundled CSV vocabulary files instead of downloading from online sources
   - Pre-packaged vocab files for multiple languages included in vocab/ directory

3. Local Administration
   - Added support for local participant folder management
   - Command-line argument for participant folder path

4. UI Adaptations
   - Modified window titles and layout for local testing
   - Added result export functionality

